        {
            "title": "舊金山房價升至創紀錄的215萬美元 AI初創企業「淘金熱」帶火樓市",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Photographer: David Paul Morris/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aTt7vpwC1NimOivc6XJCdA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/cd2f1b0ab2932a3fa174d47cab07f007\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: David Paul Morris/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 經紀公司Compass Inc.表示，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"舊金山\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:舊金山;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/舊金山\">舊金山</a>3月房屋價格中位數升至創紀錄的215萬美元，同比上漲18%。人工智能初創企業創造的財富大量湧入這座城市，推動房價大漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Compass在報告中指出，公寓價格也大幅上漲，漲幅達27%，達到136萬美元，僅略低於2022年4月創下的137.5萬美元峰值。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"舊金山房價飆升，而Zillow Group Inc.追蹤的數據顯示，3月份美國房價僅小幅上漲0.8%。攝影：David Paul Morris/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zelmDZefpxy1Pod2f0HDog--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1aa408402a898b47500c345649e050a5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">舊金山房價飆升，而Zillow Group Inc.追蹤的數據顯示，3月份美國房價僅小幅上漲0.8%。攝影：David Paul Morris/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「伊朗戰爭所帶來的經濟變化，例如利率上升和金融市場波動，並未影響舊金山極度火爆的市場格局，人工智能初創企業熱潮帶來的新增就業和財富為市場增添熱度，」Compass首席市場分析師Patrick Carlisle在報告中表示。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4a2439d8-ec01-39a8-a68d-bbcfca11d292-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">OpenAI、Anthropic PBC等人工智能公司在舊金山掀起一場新的「淘金熱」。企業員工在這座土地緊湊的城市斥資買房，但當地新房開發有限。Compass稱，3月份至少有22套房屋的售價超過500萬美元，創下單月紀錄；此外，還有24套公寓的售價超過300萬美元，同樣創下歷史月度銷售新高。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"665\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.whlTI5VlKc8dI.ySHelog--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/345cae0524ffd4e75b04d8d7bd4bc9f9\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">買家為了爭奪房源競爭激烈，房屋平均成交價比要價高出23%，追平2022年4月的溢價成交紀錄。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">舊金山房價的飆升與全美形成鮮明對比。根據Zillow Group Inc.追蹤的數據，3月份美國房價僅小幅同比上漲0.8%。舊金山房價上一次高點在2022年4月，當時購房者在利率大幅上升前急於完成交易。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題San Francisco House Prices Hit Record $2.15 Million on AI (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%88%8A%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1%E6%88%BF%E5%83%B9%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%9A%84215%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-ai%E5%88%9D%E5%89%B5%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD-%E6%B7%98%E9%87%91%E7%86%B1-%E5%B8%B6%E7%81%AB%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82-030018571.html",
