        {
            "title": "川普對伊朗最後期限臨近、停火談判受挫,油價延續漲勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hpSGRy4gF9NrZevjafYKmw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEBB70BB_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週二亞洲交易時段,油價延續漲勢,投資者為中東局勢可能升級做好準備,美國總統川普要求伊朗重新開放<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荷莫茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:荷莫茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/荷莫茲海峽\">荷莫茲海峽</a>的最後期限即將到來。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間21:08(格林威治標準時間01:08),6月到期的布蘭特原油期貨上漲0.4%至110.20美元/桶,而西德州中質原油(WTI)期貨攀升0.8%至113.32美元/桶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這是油價連續第三個交易日上漲,主要受荷莫茲海峽相關擔憂推動,該海峽是一個關鍵咽喉要道,通常承載全球約五分之一的石油運輸量。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a13acca9-37ab-3aff-9337-864fcca101fb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近幾週油輪運輸受阻,收緊了供應預期,並推高整個石油市場的風險溢價。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">緩和衝突的外交努力似乎正在受挫。伊朗拒絕了美國支持的提案,該提案概述了為期45天的停火協議、分階段重新開放海峽,以及就制裁解除和重建進行更廣泛談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗拒絕了該提案,轉而呼籲永久結束敵對行動、提供防止未來攻擊的約束性保證、取消制裁以及賠償損失。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普重申週二的最後期限堅定不移,並警告若不遵守可能促使美國打擊伊朗基礎設施,包括發電廠和橋樑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他還表示伊朗可能會被「迅速消滅」,凸顯出更大範圍升級的風險上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日益激進的言論令能源市場保持緊張,交易員正在為海灣地區進一步中斷的可能性定價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管OPEC+已採取行動適度增產,但額外供應被認為不足以抵消荷莫茲海峽中斷可能造成的損失。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%8D%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90%E8%87%A8%E8%BF%91-%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E5%8F%97%E6%8C%AB-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E5%BB%B6%E7%BA%8C%E6%BC%B2%E5%8B%A2-021215745.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-07 10:17:49",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "國際｜美伊收到停火協議框架 伊朗拒臨時停火交換開放海峽",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"國際｜美伊收到停火協議框架 伊朗拒臨時停火交換開放海峽\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">國際｜美伊收到停火協議框架 伊朗拒臨時停火交換開放海峽</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">路透引述消息人士報道，美國和伊朗已收到一份由<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"巴基斯坦\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:巴基斯坦;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/巴基斯坦\">巴基斯坦</a>擬定的停火協議方案，該方案或於周一生效，並將重新開放霍爾木茲海峽。然而，伊朗政府高級官員表示，伊朗不會以臨時停火為交換條件重新開放霍爾木茲海峽，並認為美國尚未做好實現永久停火的準備。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗政府高級官員向路透證實，已收到調解方巴基斯坦提出的最新停火提案，目前正在審閱相關內容。但該官員強調，伊朗不會接受設定最後期限或施加壓力以迫使其作出決定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報，巴基斯坦向美伊雙方提交停火協議框架，正等待雙方答覆。協議將分兩階段實施，首階段立即停火，及重新開放霍爾木茲海峽，隨後用15至20日敲定更廣泛的解決方案，達成全面協議。最終的面對面會談將在巴基斯坦首都伊斯蘭堡(Islamabad)舉行。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息人士指，最終協議預計將包括確保霍爾木茲海峽通行的區域框架，及伊朗承諾不發展核武器，以換取解除制裁和資產解凍的條款。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%8B%92%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E4%BA%A4%E6%8F%9B%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD-011741427.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-07 09:28:01",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "越共總書記蘇林當選國家主席 越南最高黨政大權罕見集於一身",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 越南國會周二選舉越共中央總書記蘇林出任<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"國家主席\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:國家主席;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/國家主席\">國家主席</a>，在他推進加強掌控並應對經濟逆風之際，越南最高黨政大權少見地集於其一人之身。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現年68歲的蘇林是這一五年任期職位的唯一候選人。在實行一黨制的越南，國會的批准在很大程度上只是履行程序。選舉結果在河內舉行的國會會議上宣布。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蘇林曾在2024年短暫兼任兩項職務，但他是首位在黨代會上正式鞏固這一「雙重角色」的領導人。越南歷史上只有少數最有權勢的領導人曾同時擔任黨內最高職務與國家主席，包括阮富仲——他在2018年時任國家主席去世後兼任該職，以及越南現代國家早期領導人胡志明。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-884b09c0-4fc4-33ee-ac0b-7e1d27763f1b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">越南的領導人結構如今更趨近於同為共產黨執政的鄰國中國。在中國，習近平同時擔任黨內最高職務與國家主席。自2024年蘇林出任越共中央總書記以來，他制定了雄心勃勃的改革議程，旨在精簡官僚體系、削減繁文縟節並清除投資障礙，以期實現國家持續成長。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Vietnam’s To Lam Secures Presidency, Tightening Grip on Power</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Nguyen Dieu Tu Uyen、Nguyen Xuan Quynh.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
